1
00:00:48,500 --> 00:00:52,620
=Endless Love=

2
00:00:52,620 --> 00:00:55,540
=Episode 23=

3
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:00,880
Ke'er.

4
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:01,759
Mo Shuo,

5
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:03,479
I need your exit token.

6
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,439
What are you going to do?

7
00:01:09,079 --> 00:01:10,000
Our fates were sealed

8
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:12,799
the moment we were born into our roles.

9
00:01:14,319 --> 00:01:15,280
Since that's the case,

10
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:17,400
what happened before

11
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:19,319
should be left in the past.

12
00:01:20,120 --> 00:01:21,120
Let's make it clean and simple.

13
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:22,719
We're done.

14
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,239
But Ling Xiao has ordered

15
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:27,000
that Mu Ruyi no longer take the Herb.

16
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,000
Everything can go back to how it was.

17
00:01:29,319 --> 00:01:30,400
Why can't you stay?

18
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:32,680
They can't go back,

19
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:36,040
and we can't either.

20
00:01:36,920 --> 00:01:38,000
If I had known

21
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,640
that restoring Mu Ruyi's memory

22
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,719
would cost you leaving me,

23
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,400
I would never have gotten involved.

24
00:01:49,159 --> 00:01:49,799
What?

25
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,400
Do you regret it?

26
00:01:55,719 --> 00:01:57,560
You never did any of this for me.

27
00:01:58,840 --> 00:02:00,040
Everything

28
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:03,159
was just a calculation on your part.

29
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:04,640
Don't you feel

30
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,840
my feelings for you?

31
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,360
Give me the token.

32
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,639
Or neither of us will have peace.

33
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:14,680
Can we just forget it and start over?

34
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,800
There's no future for us.

35
00:02:20,159 --> 00:02:21,280
Love and hate are unpredictable.

36
00:02:22,639 --> 00:02:24,680
Even if Ling Xiao had his reasons,

37
00:02:25,159 --> 00:02:26,240
his deep love

38
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,680
truly did hurt the Princess.

39
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:31,039
We're like

40
00:02:32,039 --> 00:02:33,280
the sun and the moon.

41
00:02:34,319 --> 00:02:35,599
They can never coexist.

42
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:39,159
But we are different!

43
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:41,400
The blood debt
between Dongqing and Xiling

44
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,439
cannot be erased!

45
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,919
All the peace and ease between us

46
00:02:46,599 --> 00:02:48,039
have been nothing but self-deception.

47
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:51,360
In an instant,

48
00:02:53,719 --> 00:02:54,960
nothing remained but smoke and dust.

49
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,319
Ke'er,

50
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,360
I am willing to give up my title,

51
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:03,280
as long as you stay with me.

52
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:05,919
Even if we were just common folk,

53
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,520
living in the countryside,

54
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,400
with only you and me.

55
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,319
Now that you won't help me,

56
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,159
take your sword back.

57
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:24,879
Nothing that reminds me of you

58
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:27,319
will leave the palace with me.

59
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:30,080
I'm taking none of it.

60
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,120
(Command)
Fine.

61
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:40,900
(Command)

62
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,000
Go on, then.

63
00:03:45,340 --> 00:03:45,580
(Command)

64
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:03,520
My Lady,

65
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,159
I have the token now.

66
00:04:06,439 --> 00:04:08,280
We're leaving tonight

67
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,159
to start the life we've always wanted.

68
00:04:12,319 --> 00:04:13,280
Looking back now,

69
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:16,199
I miss those carefree days.

70
00:04:17,199 --> 00:04:19,800
Here in the palace,
it's all caution and suspicion,

71
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,560
and in the end, the one closest to you
becomes the one who harms you.

72
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:23,680
My Lady,

73
00:04:24,879 --> 00:04:26,120
I really can't bear to see

74
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,120
you deceived by Ling Xiao any longer.

75
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,279
I realized it too late.

76
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,759
It's all my fault.

77
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,040
No, it's not.

78
00:04:35,759 --> 00:04:36,879
I'm the one to blame.

79
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:40,000
I should have seen

80
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:41,160
his true nature earlier.

81
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,079
Ke'er,

82
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,959
if you leave with me,

83
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,800
will you regret it?

84
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,439
My Lady,

85
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:52,959
as I said,

86
00:04:53,759 --> 00:04:55,560
I will follow every decision you make.

87
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,800
Ke'er, before we leave,

88
00:04:59,120 --> 00:04:59,839
I'll go to the kitchen

89
00:04:59,839 --> 00:05:01,319
and make him some delicacies.

90
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,199
Alright, My Lady.

91
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,480
Let me go to the kitchen
and get everything ready.

92
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,480
- Rushi.
- Ling Xiao.

93
00:05:18,319 --> 00:05:19,600
You don't have to do this.

94
00:05:20,319 --> 00:05:21,639
Just have the servants take care of it.

95
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:25,839
I've wanted to do this for a long time.

96
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:27,959
It's always been you

97
00:05:28,439 --> 00:05:29,720
looking after me,

98
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:30,920
protecting me.

99
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:33,279
Today,

100
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:36,000
while my mind is still clear,

101
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:38,199
I want to do something for you.

102
00:05:39,399 --> 00:05:40,199
Actually,

103
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:43,639
there's been something
I've wanted to tell you.

104
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:45,720
Take a seat.

105
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:47,399
Let's talk while we eat.

106
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,720
You've had so many exquisite meals.

107
00:05:58,199 --> 00:06:00,600
Are you going to
find my cooking a bit dull?

108
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,120
This is the first time

109
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:16,240
you've ever cooked just for me.

110
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,160
When I was young,

111
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,600
my mother wasn't favored.

112
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,560
I had nothing but leftovers.

113
00:06:26,439 --> 00:06:28,439
No one has ever cared about
what I like to eat

114
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,000
or what I dislike.

115
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,759
You are the supreme ruler now.

116
00:06:35,639 --> 00:06:37,759
No one would dare ignore your feelings.

117
00:06:39,759 --> 00:06:43,439
And now you have everything you want.

118
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,560
Times have changed.

119
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:47,959
It's all in the past.

120
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,560
What's with you today?

121
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:57,079
You seem different.

122
00:06:58,879 --> 00:06:59,560
I'm good.

123
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:01,839
I fell asleep just now

124
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:06,000
and had a very, very long dream.

125
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,040
I just woke up.

126
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:10,560
Whatever you dream of,

127
00:07:11,839 --> 00:07:14,639
when you wake,
I'll always be here with you.

128
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:18,839
Eat up.

129
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:20,720
Alright.

130
00:07:45,079 --> 00:07:45,639
Stop.

131
00:07:46,879 --> 00:07:48,920
A suspicious person came this way.

132
00:07:49,279 --> 00:07:50,079
Did you see?

133
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,519
No.

134
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,759
Which palace are you from?

135
00:07:54,439 --> 00:07:55,519
You look unfamiliar.

136
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,800
We are new here.

137
00:07:58,279 --> 00:07:59,319
You probably haven't seen us.

138
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,759
You're supposed to be on duty.

139
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,800
What are you doing here?

140
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:04,839
Your Highness.

141
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,680
I found two suspicious.

142
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,360
Suspicious?

143
00:08:12,519 --> 00:08:13,720
They are from my palace.

144
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,399
Since when is it your place to ask?

145
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,600
I wouldn't dare.

146
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:17,920
Get back to the city gate.

147
00:08:18,279 --> 00:08:18,800
Yes.

148
00:08:29,439 --> 00:08:30,720
Once I give something away,

149
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,919
I never take it back.

150
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:35,879
Keep this sword

151
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,279
to protect yourself.

152
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,919
Once you're out there,

153
00:08:40,399 --> 00:08:41,399
take care of yourself.

154
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:10,279
Ke'er,

155
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,440
what's on your mind?

156
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:19,240
We've returned to where we started,

157
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,360
but after everything we've been through,

158
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:26,360
it doesn't feel the same anymore.

159
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:30,639
Your Highness,

160
00:09:31,559 --> 00:09:32,919
what's on your mind now?

161
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:37,279
When Ling Xiao and I
watched the night sky,

162
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:41,879
we made wishes on the shooting stars,

163
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:44,279
promising to leave the past behind

164
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,120
and only look to the future.

165
00:09:50,440 --> 00:09:52,039
But what happened in the past

166
00:09:53,919 --> 00:09:56,759
is like a thorn embedded in my skin.

167
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,519
It can never fully heal.

168
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,039
Even if I pull it out,

169
00:10:09,639 --> 00:10:10,919
it leaves a scar

170
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,320
that hurts for a long time.

171
00:10:22,639 --> 00:10:23,320
Your Highness,

172
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:27,519
everything can start over.

173
00:10:30,279 --> 00:10:32,120
I can forget Mo Shuo too.

174
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,080
Am I right?

175
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:41,799
Your Highness,

176
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:46,039
I will always follow you.

177
00:12:00,919 --> 00:12:01,480
Mu Ruyi.

178
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:03,919
Ever since I met you,

179
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:05,600
you've always been responsive.

180
00:12:06,399 --> 00:12:07,960
You must be dealing with

181
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:09,799
something serious

182
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,279
to leave like this,

183
00:12:11,759 --> 00:12:12,519
without even a word.

184
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:17,759
From the moment you gave me the Herb,

185
00:12:17,919 --> 00:12:18,840
you should have known

186
00:12:19,519 --> 00:12:21,000
that I would find out eventually.

187
00:12:22,159 --> 00:12:23,559
Can't you stay by my side?

188
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,519
Please let me go.

189
00:12:27,159 --> 00:12:28,120
I'll let you go too.

190
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,879
Let's end it here.

191
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,039
It's better for both of us.

192
00:12:31,159 --> 00:12:31,840
I don't believe that.

193
00:12:32,519 --> 00:12:34,120
You said we could start over.

194
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:36,360
What about the future you promised?

195
00:12:37,279 --> 00:12:38,000
This time,

196
00:12:38,399 --> 00:12:40,080
we are already who we truly are.

197
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,759
It wasn't a mistake to love.

198
00:12:42,679 --> 00:12:44,120
We just hurt too much

199
00:12:44,879 --> 00:12:46,440
and needed to retreat alone.

200
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:47,720
Is that what you think?

201
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,360
Every encounter must end in parting.

202
00:12:52,679 --> 00:12:53,320
Leave.

203
00:12:53,679 --> 00:12:54,840
If you believe that walking away
without a word

204
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:56,399
is what's best for us,

205
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,000
then you've underestimated yourself,

206
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,639
and you've completely misjudged me.

207
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,480
What makes you so confident

208
00:13:02,679 --> 00:13:03,519
that I did this for you?

209
00:13:04,159 --> 00:13:05,399
I hate you with all my soul.

210
00:13:05,919 --> 00:13:06,639
The only dignity I've left you is

211
00:13:06,759 --> 00:13:08,600
that I didn't have you poisoned.

212
00:13:09,399 --> 00:13:10,559
Because it hurt too much,

213
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:12,440
you chose to tell an easier lie,

214
00:13:12,639 --> 00:13:13,279
is that it?

215
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:16,159
Every person we loved

216
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:18,320
has been slaughtered
by each other's kin.

217
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:21,279
My mother was slain by your hands.

218
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,799
How could you ask me
to face you after that?

219
00:13:24,480 --> 00:13:26,679
How could we ever speak of a future
with a clear conscience?

220
00:13:27,159 --> 00:13:29,200
Everything about us

221
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:30,759
was a curse,

222
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:32,200
nothing but a mistake.

223
00:13:32,279 --> 00:13:34,480
I never want to see you again,
for all eternity.

224
00:13:37,660 --> 00:13:41,420
♪Could there be another me somewhere♪

225
00:13:43,620 --> 00:13:45,660
(Ling Xiao's Preferences
Lui Rushi's Preferences)

226
00:13:47,060 --> 00:13:48,620
(Ling Xiao's Preferences
Lui Rushi's Preferences)

227
00:13:49,159 --> 00:13:50,320
You left this.

228
00:13:51,519 --> 00:13:52,360
Take it back.

229
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:54,799
From now on,

230
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,279
we'll never meet again.

231
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:02,180
(Ling Xiao's Preferences
Lui Rushi's Preferences)

232
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:08,980
♪They get happy endings after all♪

233
00:14:09,220 --> 00:14:14,020
♪Better to meet than to miss♪

234
00:14:14,380 --> 00:14:18,100
♪Even if just for a glance♪

235
00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:22,180
♪So many hardships in this life♪
